items.headline: Welcome to the 16 and Pregnant Wiki!
items.desc:
Welcome to the 16 and Pregnant wiki!

The 16 and Pregnant wiki is a free, public and collaborative project for all, to help create a definitive encyclopedia for the hit tv show. If you're new to 16 and Pregnant,be-aware this wiki may contains some spoilers! We are currently editing 141 articles since April 2011. We are undergoing maintenence to update some features so that we can deliver the best and reliable information for you. We welcome all editors to edit the page but please ensure the information you provide is reliable and true, as we aim to maintain the page's high standards and keep it a page that provides a reliable source of information to it's fans.

items.headline: MTV's - Teen Mom Wiki
items.desc:
Encyclopedia full of information and updates on MTV's Teen Mom cast.
Follow the lives of Teen Mom cast Maci, Farrah, Amber and Catelynn and their lives, battles and relationships and the lives of Teen Mom 2 cast Jenelle, Chelsea, Kailyn and Leah and their ups and downs.
Teen Mom has been airing it's episodes since 2009, as an update to the original 16 and Pregnant, Teen Mom chooses a select few of the Moms from 16 and Pregnant and want to continue filming. Here you will find information and truthful facts.
